title: Printer's Sample Book, "Book 9 May 1878", 1878–79
medium: Medium: leather, paper, and printed cotton textile samples
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small leather-bound book with printed textile samples. Mostly small-patterned florals and geometrics and some cretonne cloth. Predominantly browns, grays and blues.

Printer's Sample Book, "Book 9 May 1878", 1878–79.
1878–79. Medium: leather, paper, and printed cotton textile samples. Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts. 1945-55-47.
